<pre><code>Process X:
private i;
for(i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){
 a [i] = f (i);
 Exit X (R, S);
}

Process Y:
private i;
for(i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){
 Entry Y (R, S);
 b [i] = g (a [i] );
}</code></pre>
Which of the following represents the correct implementations of Exit X and Entry Y?

